testcase.name: Chelsea::Bom can render dependencies as xml
Chelsea::Deps can turn a name and version into a valid purl
Chelsea::Deps given a valid Gemfile.lock can collect dependencies
Chelsea::Deps given a valid Gemfile.lock can generate a valid coordinates object for OSS Index
Chelsea::Deps given an invalid path raises a RuntimeError with a message indicating invalid file path
Chelsea::JsonFormatter print_results brings back a valid json object
Chelsea::XMLFormatter print_results brings back a Ox xml style object
Chelsea::Gems when talking to OSS Index given a valid Gemfile.lock can collect dependencies, query, and print results
Chelsea::Gems when talking to OSS Index given an invalid Gemfile.lock will exit with a RuntimeError
Chelsea::IQClient with defaults should instantiate the client
Chelsea::IQClient with defaults with an generated dependencies sbom should be able to submit an sbom
Chelsea::IQClient with cli arguments should be able to submit an sbom
Chelsea::OSSIndex with defaults should instantiate the OSS Index client
